  		<div class = "col-md-offset-1 col-md-5 col-width">
  			<h1 class = "ind-title"> Content at your fingertips </h1><br>
  			<p class = "pull-left ind-paragraph">
  				The Open Class Knowledge Base has content from all parts of ICS 211.  From simple review topics to in-depth analysis of sorting algorithms, the Open Class Knowledge Base will have what you're looking for.
  			</p>
  		</div>
  	</div>
  	<!-- <hr> -->

  <div class = "row row-fluid row-odd">
  	<div class = "col-md-offset-1 col-md-5 col-width">
  		<h1 class = "ind-title"> Course collaboration </h1><br>
  		<p class="ind-paragraph">The Open Class Knowledge Base is driven by the peers you learn with and the instructors you learn from.  Connect, communicate, and collaborate with people you know and names you recognize.</p>
  	</div>
  	<div class="col-md-4 col-width">
  		<img class = "odd-pic center-block wow fadeInRight" data-wow-offset="420" src = "@routes.Assets.at("images/coursecollab.png")">
  	</div>
  </div>
  <!-- <hr> -->

  <div class = "row row-fluid row-even">
  	<div class = "col-md-offset-1 col-md-4 col-width">
  		<img class = "center-block wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-offset="430" src = "@routes.Assets.at("images/past.png")" onload="this.width/=1.1;this.onload=null;">
  	</div>
  	<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-5 col-width col-txt">
  		<h1 class = "ind-title">Learn from the past, prepare for the future</h1>
  		<p class = "pull-left ind-paragraph">
  			Got a question?  Chances are, someone may have already asked it. Utilize this feature and collaborate with the community to find new answers to old questions.
  		</p>
  	</div>
  </div>
  <!-- <hr> -->

