  		<p class = "pull-left ind-paragraph">
  			Open Class Knowledge Base expands on the same topics covered in class by offering different perspectives on the same problem. Go beyond the textbook and spend less time searching and more time learning.
  		</p>
  	</div>
  	<div class="col-md-4 col-width">
  		<img class = "center-block odd-pic wow fadeInRight" data-wow-offset="460" src = "@routes.Assets.at("images/designed.png")" onload="this.width/=1.1;this.onload=null;">
  	</div>
  </div>
  <!-- <hr> -->

  <div class = "row row-fluid row-even">
  	<div class = "col-md-offset-1 col-md-4 col-width">
  		<img class = "center-block wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-offset="480" src = "@routes.Assets.at("images/mobile.png")" onload="this.width/=1.1;this.onload=null;">
  	</div>
  	<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-5 col-width col-txt">
  		<h1 class = "ind-title"> Learn anywhere, anytime </h1>
  		<p class = "pull-left ind-paragraph">Access the Open Class Knowledge Base from your tablet, mobile phone, or your laptop.  Contribute content and ask questions wherever you are, whenever you want.</p>
  	</div>
  </div>
  <div class="signup-button">
